Get 50% off your first month of a monthly club with code KURZGESAGT at https://www.kiwico.com/kurzgesagt
This video was sponsored by KiwiCo. Thanks a lot for the support!

Turns out, its not birbs running kurzgesagt, but hardworking humans. Support our mission and videos by visiting the shop and getting a thoughtful product made with love: https://shop.kgs.link/love

Sources & further reading:
https://sites.google.com/view/sources-sundial/

At the height of the Cold War, a terrifying concept emerged: a bomb so powerful it wouldnt need to be dropped. Known as Project Sundial, this doomsday device would have left a 400-km radius in flames and plunged the world into darkness. It was a bomb that would destroy everything  not a weapon, but an apocalypse. How close did we come to pressing the button?
